---
---

<section class="relative py-32 lg:py-44 border-t border-border overflow-hidden">

  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] rounded-full bg-accent/5 blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6 lg:px-10">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-12 reveal">
        <span class="signal-dot"></span>
        <span class="label-accent">СТАРТУЕМ ВЕСНОЙ 2026</span>
        <span class="signal-dot"></span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="display text-[clamp(40px,7vw,112px)] mb-12 reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 100ms">
        <span class="text-text">Будь первым, кто</span>
        <br />
        <span class="text-accent">увидит первый выпуск.</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.5] text-text-dim max-w-[52ch] mx-auto mb-16 reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 200ms">
        Пиши почту — пришлю одно письмо, когда выйдет первый эксперимент.
        Никакого спама, никаких рекламных рассылок.
      </p>

      <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-[500px] mx-auto reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 300ms">
        <input
          type="email"
          required
          placeholder="your@email.com"
          class="flex-1 h-12 px-4 bg-bg-elevated border border-border-strong text-text placeholder:text-text-muted font-mono text-[14px] focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 h-12 px-6 bg-accent text-bg font-mono text-[12px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-medium hover:bg-signal transition-colors"
        >
          Подписаться
          <span class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </button>
      </form>

      <p class="mt-6 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-text-muted reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 400ms">
        Или сразу в Telegram — там ежедневный дневник
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
